madkit.message

Class EnumMessage<E extends Enum<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • madkit.kernel.Message
      • madkit.message.ObjectMessage<Object[]>
        • madkit.message.EnumMessage<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GUIMessage, KernelMessage, SchedulingMessage

    public class EnumMessage<E extends Enum<E>>
extends ObjectMessage<Object[]>
    This parameterizable class could be used to build a message tagged with an enumeration and conveying any java objects using an array of Object.

    MaDKit 5.0.0.14
